        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀美人吓！我英雄志，当初指望造鸿基。"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今，"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一旦成虚废！我项羽此行，那韩信纵有十万之众，孤家何足惧哉！只是行军之"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "际，怎生带得你行。也罢！我闻汉王乃好色之徒，你可好生扶侍他去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王说哪里话来，自古忠臣不事二君，烈女不嫁二夫。大王欲图天下大事，岂"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可以贱妾为累，愿以此身报大王之恩也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不须疑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐我三尺青锋先刎死。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀美人，你果有此心？"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果有此心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你实有此意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实有此意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢，罢，罢！我项羽就死在九泉之下，也得瞑目矣！啊呀美人，只是孤家舍你"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王舍了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王舍了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舍不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "汉兵围得紧了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪开了！哇呀……嘿！罢，罢，罢！我就把青锋付与伊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呣，老亚夫啊老亚夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王请上，妾身有一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "虞姬",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "分别去，除非梦里重相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虞姬自刎，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟离昧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王，虞娘娘自刎了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎、怎、怎么说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟离昧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虞娘娘自刎了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！啊呀美人吓！看看粉消玉碎，粉消玉碎！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 可怜一妇人，可怜一妇人，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "激烈男儿志。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甘自把身躯须臾丧我龙泉也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀美人吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 魂飞魄散，好叫我一身无计。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今，怎生区处，只恐汉兵又来至。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟离昧 （扑灯蛾） 大王休迟滞，大王休迟滞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若还不出战，及早收兵回避也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪开了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虞姬，美人……我就把……哇呀……青锋取首级。"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟离昧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "项羽 （扑灯蛾） 且将来，马上悬之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟离昧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虞姬……美人！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 愿生死同归一处，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫恁，名登青史，留下好名儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟离昧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀美人！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（项羽抛尸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看铊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟离昧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（项羽上马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "项羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘邦啊刘邦，我若拿住你的时节呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。项羽、钟离昧同下。）"
        }
      ],
